StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetShipperDischargeInforma.on]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @ShipperID int ) AS
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT [ID], [ShipperID], [DrugsUsed], [TrainingPhaseID], [Platoon], [DateRemoved], [TrainingDay], [DateReceived] FROM [USMC].[Shipper_DischargeInforma.on] WHERE [ShipperID] = @ShipperID
